.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, onion, pepper, tomato
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, jazz, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pepper        | tomato   | onion  | cucumber   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

