2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
